  "content": [
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "What is an iFrame?"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "value": "An iFrame (inline frame) is used to embed another webpage or external content within the current HTML page."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Basic Syntax"
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "language": "html",
      "value": "<iframe src=\"https://example.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\"></iframe>"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Common Attributes"
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "value": {
        "headers": ["Attribute", "Description"],
        "rows": [
          ["src", "URL of the embedded page"],
          ["width", "Width of iframe"],
          ["height", "Height of iframe"],
          ["title", "Accessibility description"],
          ["allowfullscreen", "Enable fullscreen mode"],
          ["loading", "Lazy loading (lazy/eager)"]
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Embedding YouTube Video"
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "language": "html",
      "value": "<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\"\n  src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/VIDEO_ID\"\n  title=\"YouTube video player\"\n  frameborder=\"0\"\n  allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\"\n  allowfullscreen>\n</iframe>"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Embedding Google Map"
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "language": "html",
      "value": "<iframe\n  src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!...\"\n  width=\"600\"\n  height=\"450\"\n  style=\"border:0;\"\n  allowfullscreen=\"\"\n  loading=\"lazy\">\n</iframe>"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Inline Frame Example"
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "language": "html",
      "value": "<iframe src=\"page.html\" width=\"400\" height=\"200\"></iframe>"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Security Considerations"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "value": "iFrames can pose security risks. Use attributes like sandbox to restrict behavior and ensure content comes from trusted sources."
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "language": "html",
      "value": "<iframe src=\"https://example.com\" sandbox></iframe>"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Best Practices"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "value": [
        "**Always include title for accessibility**",
        "**Use trusted sources only**",
        "**Enable lazy loading for performance**",
        "**Use sandbox for security**",
        "**Avoid excessive use of iframes**"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Common Mistakes"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "value": [
        "**Embedding insecure or unknown sources**",
        "**Not setting dimensions properly**",
        "**Ignoring accessibility (missing title)**",
        "**Overusing iframes affecting performance**"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Conclusion"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "value": "HTML iFrames are powerful for embedding external content like videos and maps. Proper use ensures security, performance, and a smooth user experience."
